Package Model.Game.Exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InsufficientTilesInPoolException
    This exception is thrown when the pool is being drawn from, but there aren't enough tiles in it.
    InvalidAmountRuntimeException
    This runtimeException is thrown when an amount of something is not valid (too high or too low).
    InvalidIdentityRuntimeException
    This runtimeException is thrown when the identity of a PutMove is invalid.
    InvalidIdRuntimeException
    This runtimeException is thrown when an ID is invalid in some way.
    InvalidMoveException
    This exception is thrown when a move is invalid.
    InvalidPositioningRuntimeException
    This runtimeException is thrown when the positioning of a PutMove is invalid.
